<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
        <div class="js-endorsements" data-for-answer="124290">
</div>

    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<p>The usort function (<a href="http://uk.php.net/manual/en/function.usort.php" rel="nofollow noreferrer">http://uk.php.net/manual/en/function.usort.php</a>) is your friend. Something like...</p>

<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title">objectWeightSort</span>(<span class="hljs-params"><span class="hljs-variable">$lhs</span>, <span class="hljs-variable">$rhs</span></span>)
</span>{
   <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-variable">$lhs</span>-&gt;weight == <span class="hljs-variable">$rhs</span>-&gt;weight)
     <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;

   <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (<span class="hljs-variable">$lhs</span>-&gt;weight &gt; <span class="hljs-variable">$rhs</span>-&gt;weight)
     <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;

   <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> -<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;
}

<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">usort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$unsortedObjectArray</span>, <span class="hljs-string">"objectWeightSort"</span>);
</code></pre>

<p>Note that any array keys will be lost.</p>
