<div class="answercell post-layout--right">
        <div class="js-endorsements" data-for-answer="71196507">
</div>

    
    <div class="s-prose js-post-body" itemprop="text">
<h3>Update from 2022 - sort array of objects:</h3>
<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">usort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$array</span>, fn(<span class="hljs-keyword">object</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$a</span>, <span class="hljs-keyword">object</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$b</span>): <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-variable">$a</span>-&gt;weight &lt;=&gt; <span class="hljs-variable">$b</span>-&gt;weight);
</code></pre>
<p>Full example:</p>
<pre class="lang-php s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-php"><span class="hljs-variable">$array</span> = [
    (<span class="hljs-keyword">object</span>) [<span class="hljs-string">'weight'</span> =&gt;  <span class="hljs-number">5</span>],
    (<span class="hljs-keyword">object</span>) [<span class="hljs-string">'weight'</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-number">10</span>],
    (<span class="hljs-keyword">object</span>) [<span class="hljs-string">'weight'</span> =&gt;  <span class="hljs-number">1</span>],
];

<span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">usort</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$array</span>, fn(<span class="hljs-keyword">object</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$a</span>, <span class="hljs-keyword">object</span> <span class="hljs-variable">$b</span>): <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> =&gt; <span class="hljs-variable">$a</span>-&gt;weight &lt;=&gt; <span class="hljs-variable">$b</span>-&gt;weight);
<span class="hljs-comment">// Now, $array is sorted by objects' weight.</span>

<span class="hljs-comment">// display example :</span>
<span class="hljs-keyword">echo</span> <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">json_encode</span>(<span class="hljs-variable">$array</span>);
</code></pre>
<p>Output:</p>
<pre class="lang-json s-code-block"><code data-highlighted="yes" class="hljs language-json"><span class="hljs-punctuation">[</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">{</span><span class="hljs-attr">"weight"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-number">1</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">{</span><span class="hljs-attr">"weight"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-number">5</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">,</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">{</span><span class="hljs-attr">"weight"</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">:</span><span class="hljs-number">10</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">}</span><span class="hljs-punctuation">]</span>
</code></pre>
<p>Documentation links:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://php.net/usort" rel="nofollow noreferrer">usort</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.php.net/manual/en/migration70.new-features.php#migration70.new-features.spaceship-op" rel="nofollow noreferrer">spaceship operator</a> (PHP 7.0)</li>
<li><a href="https://www.php.net/manual/en/migration70.new-features.php#migration70.new-features.scalar-type-declarations" rel="nofollow noreferrer">scalar type declaration</a> (PHP 7.0)</li>
<li><a href="https://www.php.net/manual/en/migration70.new-features.php#migration70.new-features.return-type-declarations" rel="nofollow noreferrer">return type declaration</a> (PHP 7.0)</li>
<li><a href="https://www.php.net/manual/en/functions.arrow.php" rel="nofollow noreferrer">arrow function</a> (PHP 7.4)</li>
</ul>
